TopicTitle: What on Earth happened to Macey Dean?

Articles.Content:
Hello, this is rdude71 and I have heard enough rumors about Macey Dean to fill a book. Some have said he is in the hospital, others have said he is dead, etc. I am actually quite worried considering that he hasn't been seen in months. Maybe some of you have information about him and we could get to the bottom of this! In addition, if didn't know already, Macey Dean is a KSP YouTuber who has made some of the most outstanding videos I have ever seen...if you haven't seen his videos, you should!

Thanks for reading, and let's hope that he's ok!

Guys, this is not the place to discuss another persons life!

This thread is closed!
